This code is a deep learning project that was made for acdemic purposes 
The Project is to detect the cancer cells in the colon by using a basic CNN model with an acuuracy of 94% 
For the use of this code firt you have to downbload the dataset used in this project (or any other agumented data set)
The dataset used in this project is Lung and Colon Cancer Histopathological Images can be found througt this link https://www.kaggle.com/andrewmvd/lung-and-colon-cancer-histopathological-images
The project is an ipynb formate, it could be imported in google colab (recommended) or in juypeter notebook. 
